WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Logera 

2
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.500
This is Dylan

3
00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:15.000
Every day, thousands of travelers just like Dylan
venture out into the world to save its beauty in
memories they will cherish forever.

4
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
For many people like Dylan,
photos are the best way to capture these memories

5
00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
But unfortunately, Dylan rarely gets a chance to capture these photos.

6
00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:28.000
Notifications from social media pull Dylan out of the moment.

7
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
In addition to this, Dylan must note details related to each of his photos
or risk forgetting them.

8
00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:41.000
This pulls Dylan further out of the moment and adds unnecessary work to his trips.

9
00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:47.000
Fortunately for Dylan, he gets to relax at the end of each day.

10
00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:55.000
Unfortunately for Dylan, he must spend this time sorting through his photos and
trying to journal about them, oftentimes while tired from a long day of travelling.

11
00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:00.000
For Dylan and thousands of others, this is frustrating.

12
00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:08.000
This is Dylan with Logera! Logera lets him easily capture all of the beautiful
places that he travels, without the hassle of having to remember the details.

13
00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:12.000
Logera also allows you to add voice captions to any photo you take.

14
00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:17.000
With this, Dylan can save what's important to him and make new memories from travelling.

15
00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:24.000
At the end of a long day of traveling, Dylan can also talk to the Logera
voice assistant like an old friend, and reflect on his day.

16
00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:30.000
The voice assistant will interact with Dylan by asking questions and showing
him photos from the day.

17
00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:33.000
With Logera, Dylan's one happy traveler!

18
00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:36.000
Logera. Your new travel companion.
